name: landrecid
description: Universally unique ID (UUID) assigned to each parcel assigned by the Land Record database.

name: parcelid
description: Parcel id assigned by the local administrative authority. AKA parcel number, APN, AIN, PID, and PIN. The format will vary.

name: parcelid2
description: Alternate parcel id assigned by the local or state administrative authority. May be the same as parcelid if no alternate given.

name: geoid
description: The full combined FIPS code of the jurisdiction in which the parcel resides (state fips + county fips).

name: statefp
description: State FIPS code.

name: countyfp
description: County FIPS code.

name: parceltype
description: Parcel type identifier or description.

name: acctnum
description: The assigned tax account number associated with this parcel / owner.

name: taxyear
description: The year for which the provided tax assessments are levied.

name: usecode
description: Land use code.

name: usedesc
description: Description of the land use associated with this parcel.

name: zoningcode
description: Zoning code associated with this parcel. These will vary in format.

name: zoningdesc
description: Zoning description associated with this parcel. These will vary in format and length.

name: numbldgs
description: Number of buildings located on the parcel. This includes primary residence as well as any accessory dwellings, garages, sheds, etc.

name: numunits
description: Number of living units located on the parcel.

name: yearbuilt
description: The recorded year that the primary building was constructed.

name: numfloors
description: Number of stories/floors/levels in the primary building according to the local authorities.

name: bldgsqft
description: Assessed area in square feet of the primary building.

name: bedrooms
description: Number of known and assessed bedrooms in the main building.

name: baths
description: Number of known and assessed bathrooms in the main building.

name: imprvalue
description: Assessed value of improvements; typically this is the value of any and all buildings located on the parcel.

name: landvalue
description: Assessed value of the surface land only. Does not include value of buildings, agriculture, or subsurface minerals or water.

name: agvalue
description: Assessed value of any agricutlure or agriculture rights.

name: totalvalue
description: Total assessed value, i.e. landvalue + imprvalue + agvalue.

name: saleamt
description: Transaction amount of the most recent recorded sale that this parcel was a part of. Usually the parcel comprises the entire sale, but occasionally the sale amount can include other parcels.

name: saledate
description: Transaction date of the most recent recorded sale that this parcel was a part of.

name: ownername
description: Name of the recorded owner.

name: owneraddr
description: Mailing address of the recorded owner, if known.

name: parceladdr
description: Mailing address of the parcel.

name: legaldesc
description: Legal description of the parcel; this is usually described in terms of lot numbers, plat numbers, book numbers, etc.

name: township
description: Public Land Survey System (PLSS) township identifier.

name: section
description: Public Land Survey System (PLSS) section identifier.

name: qtrsection
description: Public Land Survey System (PLSS) quarter-section identifier.

name: range
description: Public Land Survey System (PLSS) range identifier.

name: plssdesc
description: Public Land Survey System (PLSS) full description.

name: plat
description: Plat number or identifier

name: book
description: Plat book number or name.

name: page
description: Plat book page number or name.

name: block
description: Plat block identifier.

name: lot
description: Plat lot identifier.

name: updated
description: Date of last known update of the source data. If not specified by the source provider or if it is unknown, this field represents the date of most recent acquisition of source data.

name: centroidx
description: x-coordinate (longitude) of geographic center POINT of the parcel in EPSG 4326. In rare cases the center may lie outside the parcel shape itself in the case of a 'C'shaped parcel.

name: centroidy
description: y-coordinate (latitude) of geographic center POINT of the parcel in EPSG 4326. In rare cases the center may lie outside the parcel shape itself in the case of a 'C'shaped parcel.

name: surfpointx
description: x-coordinate (longitude) of centermost POINT that is guaranteed to lie within the parcel's surface in EPSG 4326. This point will never lie outside the parcel. Calculated using ST_PointOnSurface.

name: surfpointy
description: y-coordinate of centermost POINT that is guaranteed to lie within the parcel's surface in EPSG 4326. This point will never lie outside the parcel. Calculated using ST_PointOnSurface.

name: geom
description: MULTIPOLYGON of the parcel lot line boundary in EPSG 4326.

name: unmapped
description: A JSON object containing any remaining unmapped fields from the source data. This object is optional and may not be included for all sources, counties, or export formats.
